# Form Components

## Input Field
```jsx
<label htmlFor="email">
  Email
  <input
    id="email"
    type="email"
    placeholder="you@example.com"
    aria-describedby="email-error"
  />
  <span id="email-error" role="alert">{ERROR_MESSAGE}</span>
</label>
```

## Select Dropdown
```jsx
<select aria-label="Choose option">
  <option value="">Select...</option>
  <option value="1">Option 1</option>
</select>
```

## Checkbox
```jsx
<label>
  <input type="checkbox" role="checkbox" aria-checked="false" />
  {LABEL_TEXT}
</label>
```

## Radio Group
```jsx
<fieldset>
  <legend>{GROUP_LABEL}</legend>
  <label><input type="radio" name="group" value="1" /> Option 1</label>
  <label><input type="radio" name="group" value="2" /> Option 2</label>
</fieldset>
```

## States
- Default: `border: var(--border-default)`
- Focus: `border: var(--border-focus); outline: 2px solid var(--color-primary-200)`
- Error: `border: var(--border-error)`
- Disabled: `background: var(--bg-muted); cursor: not-allowed`
